ingredients.alim_nom_eng: Courgette or zucchini, pulp and peel, raw
Salt, white (sea, igneous or rock), iodine added, no other enrichment

ingredients_text: Lgumes (55%) (navets, carottes, courgettes, pois chiches, poivrons rouges et verts, garniture de _cleri_ ), eau, pure de tomates double concentre, sel, amidon modifi de mas, arme naturel (dont _cleri_ ), colorant : extrait de paprika.
